---

## Security Best Practices Applied
- Key-based SSH authentication
- No password-based login
- Controlled initial access
- Principle of least exposure

---

## Why This Matters
Secure instance provisioning and access control are foundational for all cloud security operations. 
Improper access configuration is a leading cause of cloud breaches.

